name: float_f32_one_tenth
description: |
  This is the nearest binary32 representation of decimal 0.1, whose exact
  value is 0.100000001490116119384765625. The paired f16 and f64 encodings are
  different approximations of the same decimal literal, exposing cross-width
  equality, promotion, serialization, and tolerance assumptions.
format: hex
decode-as: f32
pair:
  - with: ../f64/one-tenth.input
    hint: not-equal
tags:
  - "float"
  - "floating-point"
  - "ieee-754"
  - "f32"
  - "decimal-conversion"
  - "precision"
---
cd cc cc 3d   # 0x3dcccccd: nearest binary32 value to 0.1
